A massive golden CD disc cracked down the middle, transforming into sharp metallic claws grasping desperately at tiny fleeing musical notes that scatter like luminescent fireflies into a dark void. The scene is rendered in bold comic book style with heavy ink outlines, dramatic hatching, and a limited palette of deep purples, electric yellows, and stark blacks. Dynamic speed lines emphasize the desperate grabbing motion while the musical notes trail vibrant energy wisps as they escape. The composition shows the grotesque oversized hands emerging from corporate shadows below, reaching upward toward freedom and light above.
